{"title": "Story of a Needle (Version 2; Dramatic Reading)", "description": "A story told, through the viewpoint of a sewing needle, about family life and siblings. The narration from the needle tells how he was made and witnesses the relationships within the family. The needle also makes friends with a thimble and some scissors. - Summary by Susan Russell\r\n\r\nCharacters:\r\nNeedle/Narrator: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/19944\">Louise Jaeschke</a>\r\nGeorge: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/20411\">Alexandria Adair</a>\r\nMrs. Ellerslie: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/20554\">quintonreads</a>\r\nLily: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/19584\">ShrimpPhish</a>\r\nEddy: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/20549\">Levi Justus</a>\r\nThimble: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/13140\">Jenn Broda</a>\r\nMr. Ellerslie: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/15806\">czandra</a>\r\nScissors: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/14499\">mleigh</a>\r\nMr. Hardcastle: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/8425\">Larry Wilson</a>\r\nServant: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/19944\">Louise Jaeschke</a>\r\nLizzie: <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/13661\">Lynette Caulkins</a>\r\n\r\nAudio edited by <a href=\"https://librivox.org/reader/14684\">InTheDesert</a>\r\n", "duration": 8563, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "10553", "name": "Charlotte Maria Tucker (A. L. O. E.)"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/storyofaneedle_dr_2603_librivox/storyofaneedle_2603.jpg", "copyright_year": "1871", "genres": ["Dramatic Readings", "Family"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "InTheDesert"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Rapunzelina"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "JenNoel"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "My Education", "readers": [19944], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/storyofaneedle_dr_2603_librivox/storyofaneedle_01_tucker_64kb.m